pan class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">2</span> :b2<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">3</span> :b3<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">4</span> :b4<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">5</span> :b5<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">6</span> :b6<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">7</span> :b7<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">8</span> :b8<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-number">9</span> :b9<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> H ^<br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> L $<br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span>U gU <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;转换大写</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">u</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">gu</span> <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;转为小写</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">inoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-k&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Up&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">inoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-j&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Down&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">inoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-a&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Home&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">inoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-e&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;End&gt;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-j&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;t_kd&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;切换到下一条命令</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-k&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;t_ku&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;切换到上一条命令</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-a&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Home&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;转到行首</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-e&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;End&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">&quot;转到行尾</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; 窗口切换</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">j</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-w&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">j</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">k</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-w&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">k</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span>h <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-w&gt;</span>h<br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">l</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;C-w&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">l</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; vim-easy-align 对齐插件配置</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span>ga <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;Plug&gt;</span>(EasyAlign)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">&quot; NerdTree 插件配置</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">nnoremap</span> <span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;leader&gt;</span>n :NERDTreeToggle<span class="hljs-symbol">&lt;CR&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="超级用户权限编辑"><a href="#超级用户权限编辑" class="headerlink" title="超级用户权限编辑"></a>超级用户权限编辑</h2><p><code>Vim</code> 在编辑系统配置文件时经常会使用到，你也许也碰到过对一个文件编辑完成之<br>后才发现自己没有权限写这个文件。这个时候你只能使用 <code>q!</code> 丢弃编辑内容然后重 新以<br><code>sudo</code> 权限编辑文件。</p><p>幸运的是，就连这么蛋疼的问题，<code>Vim</code> 也有解决的办法，你可以使用如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">w !sudo tee &gt;/dev/null %<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
